      "text": {
        "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Problem\">Problem</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/wiki/index.php?title=2013_JBMO_Problems/Problem_1&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Problem\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Find all ordered pairs <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/8/e/8/8e8da0aef2d19017da7471378386d61620f288f5.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$(a,b)$\" style=\"vertical-align: -4px\" width=\"38\" height=\"18\" /> of positive integers for which the numbers <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/7/8/f/78f64b54fa5c88292ddfd6b0b4e398d8dfac573d.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$\\dfrac{a^3b-1}{a+1}$\" style=\"vertical-align: -14px\" width=\"58\" height=\"40\" /> and <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/6/c/8/6c8faa29157626662600f75f2ab2a012912ec2ee.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$\\dfrac{b^3a+1}{b-1}$\" style=\"vertical-align: -13px\" width=\"58\" height=\"39\" /> are both positive integers\n</p><p><br />\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Solution\">Solution</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/wiki/index.php?title=2013_JBMO_Problems/Problem_1&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Solution\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Adding <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/d/c/e/dce34f4dfb2406144304ad0d6106c5382ddd1446.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$1$\" style=\"vertical-align: -1px\" width=\"11\" height=\"14\" /> to both the given numbers we get:\n</p><p><img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/4/b/8/4b80e800f3dba2ab4b58b584adbab638d3cf2f9a.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$\\dfrac{a^3b-1}{a+1} + 1$\" style=\"vertical-align: -14px\" width=\"90\" height=\"40\" /> is also a positive integer so we have:\n</p><p><img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/4/d/b/4dbdaa19bd9f311d5290f8044543f7ce6780a08f.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$\\dfrac{a^3b+a}{a+1}$\" style=\"vertical-align: -14px\" width=\"59\" height=\"40\" /> = <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/a/0/2/a02e13e1727be25cfd7fb68a9b73cde469044ffc.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$\\dfrac{a(a^2b+1)}{a+1}$\" style=\"vertical-align: -15px\" width=\"86\" height=\"42\" /> is a positive integer\n</p><p><img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/d/7/a/d7afa79a3fb73a5c65931b86f3d2895b88562580.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$\\implies (a+1) \\mid (a^2b+1)$\" style=\"vertical-align: -5px\" width=\"187\" height=\"21\" />\n<img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/5/e/8/5e8a976815477bf39dc0a23b183da9f894a34bf7.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$\\implies (a+1) \\mid (((a+1) - 1)^2b+1)$\" style=\"vertical-align: -5px\" width=\"278\" height=\"21\" />\n<img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/a/0/f/a0fe54d74dae04356f8bc1bce77309933320839b.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$\\implies (a+1) \\mid (b+1)$\" style=\"vertical-align: -5px\" width=\"170\" height=\"20\" />\n</p><p>Similarly, \n</p><p><img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/3/d/8/3d813634de8890d7369110adae60ad33e4c99dfc.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$\\dfrac{b^3a+1}{b-1} + 1$\" style=\"vertical-align: -13px\" width=\"90\" height=\"39\" /> is also a positive integer so we have:\n</p><p><img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/f/2/5/f25fb385079a612df1dd740441947459b286c320.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$\\dfrac{b^3a+b}{b-1}$\" style=\"vertical-align: -13px\" width=\"57\" height=\"39\" /> = <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/0/6/e/06e9781884c58ec9e7dcefeb713383c26b34710f.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$\\dfrac{b(b^2a+1)}{b-1}$\" style=\"vertical-align: -15px\" width=\"84\" height=\"42\" /> is a positive integer\n</p><p><img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/8/0/9/809a40307d58c1a4b9bd99cbc704e7d23ecf8071.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$\\implies (b-1) | (b^2a+1)$\" style=\"vertical-align: -5px\" width=\"175\" height=\"21\" />\n<img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/c/b/8/cb891d37a8d8859324d3ff0f2d7e44eb010e78cc.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$\\implies (b-1) | (((b-1) + 1)^2a+1)$\" style=\"vertical-align: -5px\" width=\"266\" height=\"21\" />\n<img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/e/a/f/eaf6137c75485e0fe4b1c5f2c864d7845381710f.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$\\implies (b-1) | (a+1)$\" style=\"vertical-align: -5px\" width=\"160\" height=\"20\" />\n</p><p>Combining above <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/4/1/c/41c544263a265ff15498ee45f7392c5f86c6d151.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$2$\" width=\"8\" height=\"12\" /> results we get:\n</p><p><img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/8/6/d/86d12f51a5f5341a04f5322c7fa8791f14cedc9f.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$(b-1) | (b+1)$\" style=\"vertical-align: -4px\" width=\"110\" height=\"18\" />\n</p><p><img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/0/d/3/0d3f78e9cf5592405bd9faaf7d9c91d720865c52.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$\\implies b=2,3$\" style=\"vertical-align: -4px\" width=\"105\" height=\"18\" />\n</p><p><img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/8/3/a/83adaa30a315083ecb2a227639991791c4d1f7c3.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$Case 1: b=2$\" style=\"vertical-align: 0px\" width=\"105\" height=\"13\" />\n<img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/c/b/0/cb0dc8c211d5dbc6b82103bc464827236c7499bd.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$\\implies a+1|3 \\implies a=2$\" style=\"vertical-align: -5px\" width=\"194\" height=\"20\" /> which is a valid solution.\n</p><p><img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/1/0/1/101016cb9e750a0a9ac3c23268db22521eb7baaa.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$Case 2: b=3$\" style=\"vertical-align: -1px\" width=\"108\" height=\"14\" />\n<img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/9/c/7/9c7993d55c4ddafd90c06498cc6c68af2b597893.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$\\implies a+1|4 \\implies a=1,3$\" style=\"vertical-align: -5px\" width=\"211\" height=\"20\" /> which are valid solutions.\n</p><p>Thus, all solutions are: <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/e/6/9/e69736851cc73fa9e897d8389f21c09370e75daf.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$(2,2), (1,3), (3,3)$\" style=\"vertical-align: -4px\" width=\"135\" height=\"18\" />\n</p><p><br />\n<img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/a/b/8/ab8a050ca0f84a6aef15ead346438c2777533f30.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$Kris17$\" style=\"vertical-align: -1px\" width=\"60\" height=\"14\" />\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"Solution_1.5_(credit_to_dskull16)\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Solution_1.5_.28credit_to_dskull16.29\">Solution 1.5 (credit to dskull16)</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/wiki/index.php?title=2013_JBMO_Problems/Problem_1&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Solution 1.5 (credit to dskull16)\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>To get the two results: \n<img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/8/4/6/8462a1315e2183bab67ad368695d5ab70ce4ee7d.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$(a+1) \\mid (b+1)$\" style=\"vertical-align: -5px\" width=\"125\" height=\"20\" />\n<img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/5/d/c/5dcecce048a249813977185baf9abe02a3376d36.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$(b-1) \\mid (a+1)$\" style=\"vertical-align: -5px\" width=\"125\" height=\"20\" />\n</p><p>We can also add zero to the numerator as follows:\n</p><p><img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/a/4/5/a45d11dfd613bf3d886046c0ee37a8ed8a3bad8e.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$\\dfrac{a^3b-1}{a+1} = \\dfrac{a^3b + b - (b+1)}{a+1}$\" style=\"vertical-align: -15px\" width=\"221\" height=\"42\" />\n<img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/a/0/f/a0fe54d74dae04356f8bc1bce77309933320839b.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$\\implies (a+1) \\mid (b+1)$\" style=\"vertical-align: -5px\" width=\"170\" height=\"20\" />\n</p><p>since <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/4/d/f/4dfcebd54a691f06556d4a330d953383fc7520a3.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$a^3 + b = b(a+1)(a^2-a+1)$\" style=\"vertical-align: -5px\" width=\"230\" height=\"21\" />\n</p><p><br />\n<img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/9/0/6/906fe264bbf60d49a153696af6f101cd6e3e87f1.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$\\dfrac{b^3a+1}{b-1} = \\dfrac{b^3a - a + (a+1)}{b-1}$\" style=\"vertical-align: -15px\" width=\"224\" height=\"42\" />\n<img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/5/1/c/51c6084df40bbe55e03a80ada9d41301ed738e69.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$\\implies (b-1) \\mid (a+1)$\" style=\"vertical-align: -5px\" width=\"170\" height=\"20\" />\n</p><p>since <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/a/1/b/a1b051a2ac78a9cd32f16144fc949d1d243f4cc0.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$b^3a - a = a(b-1)(b^2 + b + 1)$\" style=\"vertical-align: -5px\" width=\"236\" height=\"21\" />\n</p><p>Then proceed as above.\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20240908025511\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.027 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.039 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 259/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 676/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 6326/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key wiki-wiki_:pcache:idhash:17118-0!canonical and timestamp 20240908025511 and revision id 216775\n -->\n"
